Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把問我這話的人打到只剩一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學生說這種話也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年過二十的小混混問這種話本身就是犯罪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 賽門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話你沒聽明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這二十年一直生活在這條街上 我變了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生活的這二十年不是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能為今後的生活注入活力 都是有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注入活力 到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我結婚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:22:11.01,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻譯：馬 翅膀 迷いの子貓  校譯：迷いの子貓 時間：木魚 後期：微音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是帝人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中要文靜的多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 現在這種樣子的孩子比較危險呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 交易是指什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的人在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？你要多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你說的是什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能承認你弟弟對張間美香所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們對美香的身體所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的是我只有情況證據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單刀直入的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 你是這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒 居然妨礙我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會原諒 妨礙我弟弟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許說出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 這個人……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂告訴我 姐姐在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須守在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為這個就有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她的身體做出那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要對我下手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個把別人的性命……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你的自我滿足就要讓矢霧同學不幸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小年紀就踏進這邊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}要是你就只會說這種無關緊要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你閉上那張讓人不快的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 可能我說的都是漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你反省殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻直到現在都無法醒悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視劇看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨說些約定俗成老套的勸說詞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是現實哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以順利進行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是什麼英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你想清楚自己有幾兩重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不對了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老套的勸說詞也好約定俗成也好沒節操也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂扯的大團圓結局都是我最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱有那種想法錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說為了他人為了世界什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 我想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 一定……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確這種想法可能很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:09:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種普通的想法 才正是大家共同考慮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說的就這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對說不通道理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒意思沒本事也沒這點腦子去挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連努力的時間都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以數量取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(送信完畢)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！這些全部都是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說 簡直就像Missing的怪奇現象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}捏他自甲田學人的「Missing」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}少爺 有您的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}你想死一次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡草 之後拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少人啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀呀第一次聚會就能有這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚇死人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Dolllars？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 艾扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了米莉亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人也都是Dollars的成員嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是啊 米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們成為現今最熱門話題的……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？難道說這些人全部都是……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 今天第一次見面的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 X N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老家的天空深遠而遼闊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩童時 在這小鎮也曾有過許多冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從何時開始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得如此平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這麼做的理由和勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在那時……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙擊 雙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 各種世界在我眼前展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道 我所無法觸及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和搬到東京的紀田聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26\frz3.24\fs24\pos(601,133)\c&H716032&\3c&HDBDBDB&}田中太郎：啊 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H2F2A62&\3c&HDBDBDB&\frz4.723\pos(302,161)}GG：我們終於考完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(381,377)\frz9.163\c&H275926&\3c&HDBDADC&}ZAWA：考試啊 好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也認識了新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\frz10.186\pos(597,336)\c&H6F6131&\3c&HDBDBDB&}田中太郎：ZAWA 畢業了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有段時間 突發奇想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初只是想製造些話題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz4.298\pos(273,198)\c&H1C4A4F&\3c&HDBDBDB&}閣下：組織？
