Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.087\pos(440,380)}Dollars？池袋才沒有這玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz16.087\pos(470,429)}虛構的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也有很多人不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}這都是聽誰說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}外人知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}混蛋 你沒來過池袋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 便會出現擁護者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz4.78\fs26\c&H1F4D52&\3c&HDBDBDB&\pos(285,164)}閣下：相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H1F4D52&\3c&HDBDBDB&\pos(318,390)\frz8.026}GG：真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H1F4D52&\3c&HDBDBDB&\pos(354,270)\frz5.963}GG：大家都相信了哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\3c&HDBDBDB&\pos(370,376)\frz9.214\c&H317237&}ZAWA：笨蛋 這些人都是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有了種不好的預感
